Tcl_Interp *  interp,
int  objc,
Tcl_Obj *CONST  objv[] 
) [friend]

Handler procedure for the tpk::axis command.

The axis command manipulates the state of a mechanism axis and takes the following forms:

  • axis <axis> enable
  • axis <axis> disable
  • axis <axis> tune par val
